---
title: Sweet Southwest Chicken Salad with Tomato & Tortilla Chips
description: This lunch idea is a new mash-up of some of our classic faves that’s sure to satisfy. You’ll toss together crisp chopped lettuce and seasoned fully cooked chicken in a honey-mustard dressing—a fun combination of delicious flavors that’s just right for a midday meal. Top it off with juicy diced tomato and crunchy blue corn tortilla chips, and you’ve got yourself one vibrant melting pot of a salad!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-southwest-chicken-salad-e6a04578.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sweet-southwest-chicken-salad-6447d75d2d4551c57307d6b0-5dac48b6.pdf
time required: 10 minutes
